msg: On the '1.7.x' branch, merge changes from the '1.7.x-r1388975' branch:
Fix for issue #4174: serf checkout/export aborts early on Windows.
Fixes issue that currently makes svn+serf+SSL on Windows unusable.
For the issue to stop occuring, serf 1.1.1 is required. This version is
not yet released, testing can be done with HEAD of serf branch 1.1.x.
